      <title>国家媒体说</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-28/china-warned-us-on-reciprocal-tariff-reprisal-state-media-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据州媒体的一份报告，中国已警告华盛顿，如果特朗普政府下周向该国征收新的互惠关税，将对美国进行报复。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-28/china-warned-us-on-reciprocal-tariff-reprisal-state-media-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Mar 2025 15:09:10 GMT</pubDate>
