    <item>
      <title>当特朗普煽动共和党攻击时，美国企业美国抛弃了绿色债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-28/corporate-america-ditches-green-bonds-as-trump-emboldens-gop-attacks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）返回白宫以来，美国公司几乎放弃了曾经被吹捧为美国企业美国掌握地球的绿色债券。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-28/corporate-america-ditches-green-bonds-as-trump-emboldens-gop-attacks</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Mar 2025 15:03:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非的DA SLAMS ANC在预算谈判中缺乏妥协</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-28/south-african-rand-weakens-after-report-of-coalition-tensions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非的民主联盟批评了非洲人国民大会不愿分享对经济政策的控制权，这使僵局升级超过了预算，这在美国联合政府中两个最大的政党之间的关系紧张。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-28/south-african-rand-weakens-after-report-of-coalition-tensions</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Mar 2025 14:58:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高盛的西班牙负责人在国家总理上写了严厉的专家</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-28/goldman-s-spain-head-wrote-scathing-op-eds-on-country-s-premier</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿尔瓦罗·德尔·卡斯塔诺（Alvaro del Castano）刚刚获得了重大晋升，成为高盛集团在伊比利亚的业务的新共同负责人。这可能终结了他作为政治专业作家炸毁当前西班牙政府的政治作家的终结。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-28/goldman-s-spain-head-wrote-scathing-op-eds-on-country-s-premier</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Mar 2025 14:54:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尼古拉创始人特雷弗·米尔顿（Trevor Milton）在欺诈定罪后被特朗普赦免</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-28/nikola-founder-milton-pardoned-by-trump-after-fraud-conviction</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位白宫官员说，尼古拉公司的创始人特雷弗·米尔顿（Trevor Milton）因其对电车制造商的财务进步而被定罪唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）赦免。]]></description>
